msgid "Your names"
msgstr "Iñigo Salvador Azurmendi"

#, kde-format
msgctxt "EMAIL OF TRANSLATORS"
msgid "Your emails"
msgstr "xalba@ni.eus"

#: hdrcalibrator.cpp:149 Main.qml:16
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:window"
msgid "HDR Calibration"
msgstr "HDR Kalibratzea"

#: Main.qml:188 Main.qml:366
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action:button"
msgid "Next"
msgstr "Hurrengoa"

#: Main.qml:195 Main.qml:372
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info accessible description of a push button"
msgid "Switches to the next page"
msgstr "Hurrengo orrira aldatzen du"

#: Main.qml:199 Main.qml:376 Main.qml:476
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action:button"
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "Utzi"

#: Main.qml:202 Main.qml:379 Main.qml:479
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info accessible description of a push button"
msgid "Cancels the calibration process"
msgstr "Kalibratzeko prozesua bertan behera uzten du"

#: Main.qml:211
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"To determine the maximum brightness of the screen, adjust the slider until "
"the logo is barely visible"
msgstr ""
"Pantailaren distira maximoa zehazteko, egokitu graduatzailea logoa nekez "
"ikus daitekeen arte"

#: Main.qml:390
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Configure how bright “100%” on the normal brightness slider should be. Make "
"it as bright as you'd ever use it, as long as the HDR image still looks good "
"and the gradients are smooth.\n"
"To avoid brightness fluctuations, it's recommended to not exceed the "
"display's maximum average brightness of %1cd/m²"
msgstr ""
"everKonfiguratu distira arruntaren graduatzailean “% 100” distira zein izan "
"behar duen. Egin ezazu erabiliko zenukeen bezain distiratsu, HDR irudia ondo "
"ikusi eta gradienteak leunak diren bitartean.\n"
"Distira fluktuazioak saihesteko, erakusleihoaren %1cd/m² gehienezko "
"batezbesteko distira ez gainditzea gomendatzen da."

#: Main.qml:392
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Configure how bright “100%” on the normal brightness slider should be. Make "
"it as bright as you'd ever use it, as long as the HDR image still looks good "
"and the gradients are smooth."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguratu distira arruntaren graduatzailean “% 100” distira zein izan "
"behar duen. Egin ezazu erabiliko zenukeen bezain distiratsu, HDR irudia ondo "
"ikusi eta gradienteak leunak diren bitartean."

#: Main.qml:439
#, kde-format
msgid "Maximum luminance: %1cd/m²"
msgstr "Gehienezko luminantzia: %1cd/m²"

#: Main.qml:460
#, kde-format
msgid "Reference luminance / paper white: %1cd/m²"
msgstr "Erreferentziazko luminantzia / paper zuriarena: %1cd/m²"

#: Main.qml:471
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action:checkbox"
msgid "Assume Windows HDR applications are calibrated for this screen"
msgstr ""
"Demagun Windows HDR aplikazioak pantaila honetarako kalibratuta daudela"

#: Main.qml:483
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action:button"
msgid "Done"
msgstr "Eginda"

#: Main.qml:492
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info accessible description of a push button"
msgid "Finish the calibration process"
msgstr "Kalibratzeko prozesua bukatu"

#: Main.qml:501
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Many Windows applications come with their own calibration settings, which "
"this system wide configuration conflicts with. If this option is set, their "
"calibration settings will work as expected on this specific display."
msgstr ""
"Windows aplikazio askok beren kalibrazio-ezarpen propioak dituzte, eta "
"sistema osorako konfigurazio honek haiekin gatazka du. Aukera hau ezarrita, "
"gailu jakin honetan, haien kalibrazio ezarpenak espero bezala ibiliko dira."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "To determine the maximum average brightness of the screen, adjust the "
#~ "slider until the logo is barely visible"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Pantailaren gehienezko batezbesteko distira zehazteko, egokitu "
#~ "graduatzailea logoa nekez ikus daitekeen arte"

#~ msgid "Maximum fullscreen luminance: %1cd/m²"
#~ msgstr "Pantaila osoko gehienezko luminantzia: %1cd/m²"
